Package: bankcheck
Type: Project
Title: Bank Check
Version: 1.0.0
Description: Dependency manifest for the Bank Check Shiny app. Not an R
    package; this file declares the app's direct runtime dependencies so
    renv can snapshot them (type = "explicit") into renv.lock, which CI
    restores for testing and both deploys. Deploy-only tooling (shinylive,
    rsconnect) is installed unpinned in the workflows and deliberately
    left out of Imports.
Imports:
    shiny,
    bslib,
    plotly,
    dplyr,
    DT,
    commonmark,
    jsonlite,
    htmltools
